page.title: 09A TYPICAL WEEKDAY-CHILD
page.content: At 7:30am,I get up and get dressed and go down for breakfast.When 8:30 comes we go to school.Sometimes we have assembly with Mr.Taylor. After assembly we go to our class rooms.We normally do maths until 10:40. When playtime is finished we go in and Mr.Talor talks to us until lunchtime. After lunch play we go in and do some work. At 2:30 we have play and after play we have a story. After School we have Drama.It finishes at 4:15. I then go home and have tea and watch TV.At 7:15 I go to Guides until 9:00.When I get home I have my Supper.Then I have a bath and go to bed.
